        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段揚升 恒指漲350點報26958點 阿里巴巴升4.99%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股昨晚於外圍急升，直接帶動港股氣氛。恒生指數今早開市直逼萬七關口，以26958點開市，升350點或1.32%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5976點，升113點或1.93%；國企指數以9335點開市，升115點或1.25%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股幾乎全線造好，阿里巴巴(09988)ADR昨晚折合每股收市已較股份在港升逾5%，該股今早開報162元，漲1.99%；騰訊(00700)開報637元，升2.25%；美團(03690)開報106.5元，升1.43%；京東(09618)開報119.3元，升2.05%；小米(01810)開報39.28元，升1.39%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於兩大藍籌國際金融股，滙控(00005)今早開報126.2元，漲1.69%；友邦(01299)開報85.05元，升1.61%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥明康德(02359)發盈喜，料去年純利升逾倍；該股今早開報116元，漲4.69%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source-web_02359-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source-web_02359-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日共有3隻新股掛牌，今早全部高開。在GEM上市的BBSB(08610)以3元開市，較招股價0.6元高4倍。在兩隻主板掛牌新股中，紅星冷鏈(01641)開報19.58元，較招股價12.26元高59.71%；兆易創新(03986)開報235元，較招股價162元也高45.06%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15577650-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%bc%b2350%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126958%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e5%8d%874-99",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-13 09:30:35",
