            "title": "即月期指開報27015點 高水407點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報27015點，升418點，較上日現貨收市價26608點高水407點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5986點，升123點，高水123點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9347點，升135點，高水127點。</p>\n</div>",
